{"name":"Grendelle the Aggrandised","size":"large","type":"fey","tag":"Empowered Hag","alignment":"neutral evil","hitDice":"15","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":7,"otherArmorDesc":"17 (natural armor)","speed":"40","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"20","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"112 (15d8 + 45)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"15","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"16","wisPoints":"14","chaPoints":"18","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"120","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"60","telepathy":0,"cr":"8","customCr":"3 (700 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"[MON] can take 2 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent legendary actions at the start of her turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, Grendelle can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), Grendelle can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The grapple action may not happen two turns in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the green hag's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the green hag's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the green hag dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Amphibious","desc":"[MON] can breathe air and water."},{"name":"Magic Resistance","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects."},{"name":"Immutable Form","desc":"[MON] is immune to any spell or effect that would alter her form."},{"name":"Mimicry","desc":"[MON] can mimic animal sounds and humanoid voices. A creature that hears the sounds can tell they are imitations with a successful DC [CHA SAVE] Wisdom (Insight) check."},{"name":"Innate Spellcasting","desc":"[MON]'s innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE]). She can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:\n\n\n> At will: _Guiding Bolt, Dancing Lights, Thaumaturgy, Vicious Mockery, Speak With Plants_\n> 4/day: _Blinding Smite, Ray of Enfeeblement, Blindness, Moonbeam_\n> 2/day: _Fear, Sickening Radiance, Charm Monster_\n> 1/day: _Tree Stride, Dream_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] uses Shimmerpulse, then makes two Claw or Slam attacks."},{"name":"Claws","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 10 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 2d12] slashing damage."},{"name":"Slam","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 3d4] bludgeoning damage and the target must make a [STR SAVE] dexterity saving throw or fall prone."},{"name":"Shimmerpulse","desc":"Tendrils of energy erupt from [MON] and batter all creatures within 10 feet of her. Each creature in that area must make a dc [CHA SAVE] Strength saving throw. On a failed save, a target takes 2d6 necrotic damage and can’t take reactions until its next turn. On a successful save, the creature takes half damage, but suffers no other effect."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Starry Gaze","desc":"[MON] levels her gaze at one creature within 60 ft. It must succeed on a DC [CHA SAVE] Wisdom saving throw or become frightened for 1 minute. A creature can repeat the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. Once a creature succeeds it is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours."},{"name":"Blinding Smite","desc":"_concentration, 1 minute_: The next time [MON] hits a creature with a melee attack, it must make a DC [CHA SAVE] constitution save and take [3d6] additional radiant damage and be blinded for the duration. A creature which succeeds takes half as much damage and is not blinded."}],"reactions":[{"name":"Reactive Lash","desc":"When a creature hits [MON] with a melee attack, she can use her reaction to attempt to grapple the creature."}],"legendaries":[{"name":"Piercing Tendril (Recharge 6)","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [STR 3d8] piercing damage and the target must make a DC [STR SAVE] constitution saving throw or take [4d8] necrotic damage. A creature which succeeds takes half as much necrotic damage. Regardless, the creature's maximum hp is reduced by the necrotic damage taken in this way for 1 hour."},{"name":"Aurora Wall","desc":"[MON] conjures a wall of light 60ft long. A creature which has not succeeded on the _Starry Gaze_ save cannot willingly approach the wall. The wall vanishes at the start of Grendelle's next turn."},{"name":"Relocate Spell","desc":"[MON] can move _Moonbeam_ or _Sickening_ radiance to another point within range."},{"name":"Guiding Bolt (1/round)","desc":"_Ranged Spell Attack:_ [CHA ATK] to hit, range 120 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [4d6] radiant damage, and the next attack roll against the creature has advantage."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"wis","order":4},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"arcana","stat":"int"},{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"necrotic","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"},{"name":"radiant","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"},{"name":"invisible"},{"name":"poisoned"}],"languages":[{"name":"Abyssal","speaks":true},{"name":"Aire","speaks":true},{"name":"Common","speaks":true},{"name":"Deep Speech","speaks":true},{"name":"Dwarvish","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Grendelle","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":8,"damage":[]}